No intent of keep beating a dead horse, but with the Venom trailer that just came out, I couldn&#039;t evade thinking; &quot;Yeah. I think this is the image that comes to most of us when thinking on an alien parasite bonded to a human.&quot;

Tom Hardy is clasically good loking, and still can look horrifying when the symbiote comes out. So at least, when her helmet comes down, we could get a better idea of an alien creature twisting and bonding with her body with a feature like that, instead of just looking like she just is wearing a grey scaled body suit.
